text: Called out! Kylie Jenner's ex - boyfriend, Tyga, unexpectedly called Kim Kardashian out in her Instagram comments on Tuesday, and fans are ( unsurprisingly ) flipping out about it. Kardashian and her sisters recently returned from Japan, and the KKW Beauty founder continued to share photos from their Instagram - dominating trip on social media on Tuesday. In one of the grainy shots, Kardashian is wearing a dark ensemble at a train station in Kyoto, which she accidentally misspelled as Keyoto.
